the first hero of the Dalin Three Heroes.

46
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,860
So the name Huo Dongfeng is very fitting.

47
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,600
What about the villain?

48
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,280
Didn't I tell you already?

49
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:57,020
Gou Changzi and Dong Yingren.

50
