81
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:07,360
Very well.

82
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,300
Alright, hurry up now.

83
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:15,800
How long has it been?

84
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,120
