87
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,280
Listen to me.

88
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:27,040
The Criminal Procedure Law of the People's Republic of China,

89
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,480
Article 156 states that

90
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:31,120
