92
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,240
must not exceed 2 months.

93
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,480
For serious cases,

94
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,640
with the prosecutor's approval,

95
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,840
