96
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:39,840
Am I right?

97
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,480
But how long has it been already?

98
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,360
You're right.

99
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:45,220
