123
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,840
Besides,

124
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:15,240
didn't you,

125
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:15,720
in college,

126
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,480
study something about

127
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,940
spacecraft or something?

128
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,840
How come you know these legal articles

129
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:19,480
so well?

130
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,760
I just took the bar exam.

131
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:21,560
What?

132
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,600
You're becoming a lawyer?

133
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,120
Yes. That lawyer you introduced me to

134
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,880
