135
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,960
I really regret it.

136
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,480
I feel so guilty.

137
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,600
If I hadn't been so loose-lipped back then,

138
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,600
