143
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,200
Stop talking nonsense.

144
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,360
Do you have any solutions?

145
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,159
We need to figure something out!

146
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:43,240
Yes, there is one way.

147
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,690
Go study criminal investigation.

148
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:46,720
If you catch the real killer,

149
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,880
