151
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:50,960
I'm not messing with you.

152
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,820
I think you could really learn it.

153
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,120
Criminal investigation is your job.

154
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,240
Yes, it is our job.

155
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,000
We all believe

156
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,659
Guo Dapao is the real culprit.

157
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:58,940
Anything else?

158
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,640
I'm leaving.

159
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,120
I'm busy.

160
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,650
Brother.

161
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,760
Remember that little girl

162
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:12,690
