163
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,240
I already paid the bill.

164
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,480
Has she been back?

165
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:16,360
She's been here twice.

166
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,240
Just wandering outside the door.

167
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,080
Too scared to come in.

168
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:18,760
When I called out to her,

169
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,220
she ran away immediately.

170
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,360
This kid.

171
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,360
Next time,

172
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,200
grab her

