174
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,560
Let her eat until she's full.

175
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:28,720
Alright.

176
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,960
Grill me 30 skewers,

177
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,480
