178
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,610
I'll take them to go.

179
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:33,840
Okay.

180
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,420
Make it 50 skewers.

181
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,360
Sure, sure.

182
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,880
Last time, I was chatting with Guo Dapao here.

183
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,960
I told him to find

184
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,120
