Did you hear that?

186
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,640
No, what's up?

187
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,720
It's fine.

188
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,560
What did Grandpa say?

189
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,440
He said

190
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,360
he won't let me eat at this kebab place

191
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,600
because last time

192
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,640
after you took me for kebabs

193
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:05,200
I had diarrhea for days.

194
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,320
You're eating too fast.

195
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,240
Slow down.

196
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:11,360
Uncle, I'm getting my lawyer's license soon.

197
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,120
When that happens,

198
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:14,320
I can personally defend Dalei in court.

199
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,560
Mr. Cui,

200
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,480
did you know that Huo Xiaoyang

201
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,080
