212
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,370
My classmate is pressing me for it.

213
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,460
How much have you written?

214
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:53,980
I still need to write 20,000 to 30,000 words out of 100,000.

215
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,480
What's the title?

216
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,700
'Cleansing the Sword in the Vast Sea'

217
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,890
That's a good title.

218
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,840
Has the factory contacted you recently?

219
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,970
No contact. Why would they contact me?

220
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,320
My lawyer's license is coming soon.

221
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:14,240
I'll be a lawyer then.

222
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:14,960
Who wants to mess around with them

223
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,420
