224
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:21,200
Children grow up and make their own decisions.

225
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:22,760
You're on your own now.

226
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:26,840
You're always talking about breaking through bottlenecks.

227
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,120
I've gotten used to it.

228
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,730
Just remember this.

229
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:32,000
You're not alone.

230
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:35,240
