231
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:38,000
Other families with just one child might manage,

232
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,200
but you have two!

233
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:44,560
There might be more than two in the future.

234
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,480
Who else?

235
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,880
I'm just kidding.

236
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,480
To continue our story...

237
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:05,120
That day, Huo Dongfeng was walking through a small grove.

238
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,120
He discovered a female warrior

239
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,840
lying in the grove.

240
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:15,880
This female warrior

241
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,720
was young and beautiful.

242
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:21,010
Huo Dongfeng was immediately stunned by her beauty.

243
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:27,120
Then Huo Dongfeng took out

244
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,600
his special antidote.

245
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,600
But

246
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:38,760
when the female warrior woke up,

247
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:41,200
she mistakenly thought Huo Dongfeng

248
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,930
was the one who had stabbed her.

249
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,810
So the female warrior immediately drew her sword

250
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:50,040
and stabbed at Huo Dongfeng.

251
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:52,480
Such ingratitude!

252
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,200
What a pity.

253
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,260
What happens next?

254
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,880
Huo Dongfeng was stabbed

255
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:01,240
and left dying by the female warrior.

256
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:04,440
It was then that the female warrior realized

257
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,570
she had wrongly accused Huo Dongfeng.

258
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,840
So then,

259
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:13,120
the female warrior found a swift horse,

260
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,720
and the two of them rode together

261
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,240
to her home.

262
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:19,760
Then, over several months,

263
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,840
under the female warrior's care,

264
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:24,200
Huo Dongfeng's wounds finally healed,

265
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:28,200
and he regained 90% of his martial powers.

266
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,000
That's a relief.

267
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,360
That's so tragic.

268
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:33,290
Did the female warrior and Huo Dongfeng get married?

269
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,320
I'll tell you about that tomorrow.

270
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,120
Let's continue tomorrow.

271
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,360
Is this a good story?

272
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:44,620
And what's the name of the female warrior in this story?

273
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,240
She must have a name, right?

274
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,960
Yes, tell us quickly.

275
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,240
That's right.

276
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,120
Exactly.

277
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,360
Tell us now.

278
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:51,960
Go on.

279
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:56,200
Cui Xiaohong.

280
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,480
Uncle.

281
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:03,210
Did the heroine and Huo Dongfeng end up together?

282
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:06,360
It's a secret.

283
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:09,100
How's your dance practice going?

284
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:09,880
Very well.

285
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,120
Show us.

286
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:46,000
Very good! With my level of expertise,

287
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:47,760
I can't really point out anything wrong

288
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:49,090
