598
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,200
not for you.

599
00:22:05,360 --> 00:22:06,360
This...

600
00:22:06,360 --> 00:22:07,240
Hurry.

601
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,840
What a loud voice!

602
00:22:08,840 --> 00:22:10,360
He'll achieve great things in the future.

603
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:11,000
Keep it down,

604
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:11,800
