609
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,780
Enjoy your drinks.

610
00:22:19,800 --> 00:22:20,600
Oh, by the way,

611
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:23,320
I'll have some good news for you in a few days.

612
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:24,720
What good news?

613
00:22:24,720 --> 00:22:25,880
Tell us now!

614
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:27,560
I'll tell you in a few days.

615
00:22:27,560 --> 00:22:29,020
Enjoy your drinks for now.

616
00:22:29,560 --> 00:22:31,490
Alright, take care, Manager Tang.

617
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:32,480
I mean,

618
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:33,400
such a big guy

619
00:22:33,400 --> 00:22:34,560
doesn't know his own strength.

620
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:36,220
Why are you making such a fuss?

621
00:22:37,040 --> 00:22:38,520
He's just a manager.

622
00:22:38,600 --> 00:22:40,400
