626
00:22:45,360 --> 00:22:45,800
No, well...

627
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,720
How can he compare to Old Cui?

628
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:49,720
We should respect people who deserve it.

629
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:50,760
Just look at him.

630
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:52,480
He doesn't look like a good person, right?

631
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:54,000
