632
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,280
As if you're such a good person yourself.

633
00:22:55,280 --> 00:22:55,640
Listen to yourself.

634
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:56,320
I'm not a good person.

635
00:22:56,320 --> 00:22:57,520
