638
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:01,040
I'm not a good person.

639
00:23:01,040 --> 00:23:02,700
I'm not a good person. Come on.

640
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:03,640
Let's eat.

641
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:04,480
Try some of these braised dishes.

642
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:06,610
These are the only decent things here.

643
00:23:06,800 --> 00:23:07,720
The child is so cute.

644
