Looks like a little piglet.

645
00:23:10,560 --> 00:23:11,120
What?

646
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:18,360
I really envy you,

647
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:20,560
not having to worry about anything.

648
00:23:20,560 --> 00:23:21,480
Look at me,

649
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:24,120
helping my sister raise my nephew.

650
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:25,040
Now

651
00:23:25,120 --> 00:23:26,880
I've got Guo Dapao's daughter

652
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,610
and her father to deal with too.

653
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:32,200
I wish I could be like you,

654
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:34,370
doing math problems every day,

655
00:23:35,040 --> 00:23:36,120
carefree

656
