662
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,080
He broke the pinhole glasses

663
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:02,560
that I borrowed from my deskmate.

664
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:03,640
I told him many times

665
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,280
not to let him play with them,

666
00:24:04,280 --> 00:24:05,210
but he insisted.

667
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:06,600
Glasses?

668
00:24:06,760 --> 00:24:07,720
So they're broken.

669
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,760
Can't we just buy another pair?

670
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:09,600
Exactly.

671
00:24:10,040 --> 00:24:11,400
This is high-tech stuff,

672
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,660
it costs over 100 yuan.

673
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:15,120
Alright, come on.

674
00:24:15,120 --> 00:24:16,720
Come inside.

675
00:24:32,320 --> 00:24:33,600
What high-tech stuff?

676
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:35,520
This costs over 100?

677
00:24:36,040 --> 00:24:36,800
Why?

678
00:24:38,560 --> 00:24:40,120
They say it's high-tech

679
00:24:40,600 --> 00:24:42,330
and can cure nearsightedness.

680
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:44,400
I really didn't mean to.

681
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,080
Okay, don't cry.

682
00:24:46,080 --> 00:24:47,340
We'll buy another one.

683
00:25:10,800 --> 00:25:13,600
Those pinhole glasses are popular in schools now.

684
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:16,330
And my uncle spotted a business opportunity.

685
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:28,040
My uncle and aunt

686
