689
00:25:34,760 --> 00:25:35,820
It doesn't matter.

690
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:38,980
Why doesn't it matter?

691
00:25:39,040 --> 00:25:41,040
Whether my dad is chasing dogs or chickens,

692
00:25:41,040 --> 00:25:42,640
is it really that important?

693
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,820
This time it's really promising.

694
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:48,040
Didn't you say the same thing about writing novels last time?

695
00:25:48,040 --> 00:25:49,520
I bet it won't work out.

696
00:25:50,120 --> 00:25:52,050
You two are always ganging up on me.

697
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:03,480
Dad's cooking is still the best.

698
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:06,210
The food at Dingqing Restaurant is terrible now.

699
00:26:07,040 --> 00:26:09,120
You come here in the middle of the night

700
00:26:09,120 --> 00:26:11,200
just to complain

701
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:13,720
that Dingqing Restaurant's food tastes bad?

702
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,760
I can't do anything about it anymore.

703
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:16,480
No, no,

704
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:17,810
that's not why I'm here.

705
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:21,080
Dad, look at this.

706
00:26:21,280 --> 00:26:23,740
Aren't these the glasses that Erpang broke?

707
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,200
Why are they like this again?

708
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,560
You two are really something, father and son.

709
00:26:26,560 --> 00:26:27,890
I want Dad to take a look.

710
00:26:28,040 --> 00:26:28,840
What is this?

711
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:30,040
Where are the lenses?

712
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:31,840
Erpang broke them.

713
00:26:32,080 --> 00:26:33,340
Just look at that part.

714
00:26:34,040 --> 00:26:35,040
Try them on.

715
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,240
It gives you that 'seeing through a tube' feeling,

716
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,760
right? But this one

717
00:26:43,080 --> 00:26:44,560
is what they call

718
00:26:44,560 --> 00:26:46,400
high-tech pinhole glasses.

719
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:48,800
They sell for over 100 yuan outside.

720
00:26:48,800 --> 00:26:49,560
This...

721
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:51,720
What's so high-tech about this?

722
00:26:51,720 --> 00:26:52,840
You're absolutely right!

723
00:26:52,840 --> 00:26:54,200
I've been studying it all day.

724
00:26:54,200 --> 00:26:55,400
