729
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:03,200
are available everywhere.

730
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:05,520
So, I have a bold idea.

731
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:07,450
You've got another one?

732
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:09,560
How long has it been since your last scheme?

733
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:10,800
You've sold singing performances,

734
00:27:10,800 --> 00:27:11,560
set up chess stalls,

735
00:27:11,560 --> 00:27:13,160
written books, and now what?

736
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:14,280
Selling glasses?

737
00:27:15,040 --> 00:27:16,120
It's like this.

738
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:17,450
The cost of these things

739
00:27:17,760 --> 00:27:18,890
is only about 5 yuan.

740
00:27:19,280 --> 00:27:21,360
But they sell them for over 100 yuan in the market.

741
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:22,960
What an outrageous profit margin!

742
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,240
Aren't they just profiteers?

743
00:27:24,240 --> 00:27:25,400
Isn't this taking advantage of people?

744
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:26,560
Over 100 yuan for

745
00:27:26,560 --> 00:27:27,560
an average family

746
00:27:27,560 --> 00:27:29,320
is not something everyone can afford.

747
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:30,280
What I want to do

748
00:27:30,280 --> 00:27:31,800
is bring down the price

749
00:27:31,800 --> 00:27:33,560
