750
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:36,170
can wear affordable pinhole glasses.

751
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:38,760
So you're saving all the kids in the city?

752
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:41,160
I want to save children across the country!

753
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:43,320
I'll price them at 19.9 yuan,

754
00:27:43,320 --> 00:27:44,720
not even 20 yuan.

755
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:46,560
