764
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:00,880
What I want to do is different.

765
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:02,760
I create value for society,

766
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:04,400
make a contribution,

767
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:06,200
and earn money at the same time.

768
00:28:06,320 --> 00:28:07,840
