769
00:28:07,840 --> 00:28:08,880
It's three birds.

770
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:11,880
How much money do you need?

771
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:13,080
100,000 for startup capital.

772
00:28:13,080 --> 00:28:14,320
