827
00:30:15,360 --> 00:30:16,920
I know your abilities.

828
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:18,400
You should

829
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:19,920
combine your talents

830
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:21,840
