840
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:43,800
I've already booked tickets

841
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,460
to Wenzhou to purchase stock.

842
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,760
You're moving so quickly.

843
00:30:47,840 --> 00:30:48,800
In martial arts,

844
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:50,000
speed is unbeatable.

845
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:52,000
Just watch me.

